DVD Audio:
Notes: This release is a Hybrid DVD Audio Disc and does not contain any video. It can only be played on a DVD player.

Jewel Case
The fifth release in 1979 from Alan Parsons Project after the string of successful releases including I Robot, Pyramid and Eve. The songs include: Games People Play, Time, Nothing Left to Lose and the title track among others. This album unlike most plays front to back with one great tune after another. Not to be missed if you grew up in the 70&#039;s and even if you didn&#039;t.
